	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />2600 has 2 channels, what I like about them is that they have this crazy-ass distortion setting (4-bit), one setting makes a square wave, the others range between noise and some combination of square + pseudo-random.
<br />
<br />It's a shame the frequency range is horrible.
<br />
<br /><a href="http://qotile.net/files/2600_music_guide.txt" class="postlink">http://qotile.net/files/2600_music_guide.txt</a>
<br />
<br />DMC channel might do alright with some of them maybe, pulse channels would be pretty weak though for reproducing settings besides the square.  The $4011 DAC would work good, of course.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


