	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />It's basically as simple as something like this :
<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">.org $8000<br />include &quot;MySong.raw&quot;<br /><br />PlayDMC:<br />&nbsp; ldy #$00<br />&nbsp; sty Pointer<br />&nbsp; lda #$80<br />&nbsp; sta Pointer+1<br />- nop<br />&nbsp; nop&nbsp; &nbsp; &#40;as many NOP as you want in function of the frequency&#41;<br />&nbsp; nop<br />&nbsp; lda &#91;Pointer&#93;,Y<br />&#40;&#40;add potential decompressioon algorithm, format converting and end of sample checks here&#41;&#41;<br />&nbsp; sta $4011<br />&nbsp; iny<br />&nbsp; bne -<br />&nbsp; inc Pointer+1<br />&nbsp; bne -<br />etc....</div>

		

		</td>
	</tr>
